    #why-dogeparty.section.why-dogeparty
      .container
        .row
          .col-xs-12
            %h2.headline.text-center Why Dogeparty?
            %p.text-center
              Bitcoin-based Counterparty is a fantastic system for serious crypto-finance, but for smaller
              value transactions, when it comes to placing orders, creating assets, and generally taking care
              of business DOGE brings some great advantages to the party.

      %ul.container.profits
        %li.row
          .col-xs-12.col-sm-4.text-center
            %img.img-stop-watch{alt: "10x Faster", src: "assets/images/stop-watch@2x.png"}/
          .col-xs-12.col-sm-8
            %h3.showable-toggle
              %span 10x Faster
              .toggle-icon.visible-xs
                %strong.plus +
                %strong.minus -
            %p.showable
              Transactions confirmation times on Dogeparty are typically 10x faster than traditional Bitcoin
              transactions, at 1-10 minutes. This opens the door to whole new applications impossible with slower network speeds.

        %li.row
          .col-xs-12.text-center.visible-xs
            %img.img-piggy{alt: "100x Cheaper", src: "assets/images/piggy@2x.png"}/
          .col-xs-12.col-sm-8
            %h3.showable-toggle
              %span 100x Cheaper
              .toggle-icon.visible-xs
                %strong.plus +
                %strong.minus -
            %p.showable
              Network fees on a meta-layer can be around $0.25, and make it costly to run applications on top of Bitcoin. DOGE fees are about 100x cheaper, so micro-transactions can thrive on Dogeparty, ideal for socially-oriented projects and startups.
          .col-xs-4.text-center.hidden-xs
            %img.img-piggy{alt: "100x Cheaper", src: "assets/images/piggy@2x.png"}/

        %li.row
          .col-xs-12.col-sm-4.text-center
            %img.img-hands{alt: "Friendly", src: "assets/images/hands@2x.png"}/
          .col-xs-12.col-sm-8
            %h3.showable-toggle
              %span Friendly
              .toggle-icon.visible-xs
                %strong.plus +
                %strong.minus -
            %p.showable
              With Dogeparty you can take part in an community-driven global marketplace of good, where anything and
              everything is traded with no exchange fees. If this is a message that resonates with you, weâ€™d love your support.

