            %p
              XDP is fuel for the Dogeparty rocket. Buy the fuel with your DOGE during the burn period. With XDP you can
              issue your own custom tokens for e-tickets, reward points, game currencies &amp; so on.

      %ul.container.xdp-workflow.showable
        %li.row
          .col-xs-12.col-md-4.text-center.hidden-md.hidden-lg
            %img.img-doge-on-fire(alt="Proof of Burn" src="assets/images/doge-on-fire@2x.png")/
          .col-xs-10.col-xs-offset-1.col-sm-12.col-sm-offset-0.col-md-8
            %h3
              %span How does
              %span.nowrap Proof of Burn work?
            %p
              The burn involves sending DOGE to a provably unspendable address (it might look a bit like DOGEPARTYxxxxxxx) effectively destroying the DOGE.
            %p
              For every 1000 DOGE you burn, you will receive 1 XDP. To reward earlier burners, the first blocks will award a bonus of 50%, giving you
              back 1.5 XDP for every 1000 DOGE. This is a bonus that gets a little bit lower with each block that passes, by the end of the burn
              the rate will be exactly 1000:1. After burning your DOGE, the issuance of your XDP will happen automatically by the protocol.
            %p
              The burn begins on Tue, August 12th and will last for 30 days. There will only ever be one burning period, so get 'em while they're hot!
              If you're thinking about creating something on Dogeparty, you'll need to obtain some XDP. It should be possible to get some later, but
              you'd need to buy it from someone selling on an exchange&mdash;likely at a higher price.
          .col-xs-12.col-md-4.text-center.hidden-xs.hidden-sm
            %img.img-doge-on-fire(alt="Proof of Burn" src="assets/images/doge-on-fire@2x.png")/

        %li.row.xdp-diy
          .col-xs-12.col-md-4.text-center
            %img.img-to-the-moon(alt="How do I get started?" src="assets/images/to-the-moon@2x.png")/
          .col-xs-10.col-xs-offset-1.col-sm-12.col-sm-offset-0.col-md-8
            %h3 How do I get started?
            %ul.steps.text-left
              %li
                .num 1
                %span You'll need to get yourself a Dogewallet, our custom version of Counterwallet. It will be available
                when the counter above reaches zero.
              %li
