                %span Send DOGE from your existing wallet to one of the addresses in Dogewallet.
              %li
                .num 3
                %span The wallet shows your sent balance in DOGE. Click on the menu and choose the 'Burn' entry, select an amount and you are ready to go.
              %li
                .num 4
                %span Congratulations! You've got XDP.


